1
00:01:36,646 --> 00:01:39,879
[Episode 23]

2
00:01:39,879 --> 00:01:42,439
When exactly will you
practice your needling technique?

3
00:01:42,439 --> 00:01:44,319
The Suwen Assembly is coming up soon.

4
00:01:44,319 --> 00:01:47,560
The whole clan will be there to watch.

5
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:49,080
Don't embarrass yourself.

6
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:50,199
Little Bai.

7
00:01:50,199 --> 00:01:53,920
Just wait for your brother
to win at the Suwen Assembly.

8
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:56,479
Stop daydreaming.

9
00:01:56,479 --> 00:01:59,537
Go review your books, will you?

10
00:02:01,439 --> 00:02:02,560
Fine.

11
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,920
Little Bai.

12
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:08,375
Do as you say, I'll go and study hard.

13
00:02:09,959 --> 00:02:11,399
Wait.

14
00:02:11,399 --> 00:02:13,079
Where are you going?

15
00:02:13,079 --> 00:02:14,880
Don't go looking for Sister Qiu Chan.

16
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:17,999
Uncle Xiang Cai said the plague outside
is getting worse.

17
00:02:17,999 --> 00:02:19,759
Don't get infected.

18
00:02:19,759 --> 00:02:21,891
Little Bai.

19
00:02:21,891 --> 00:02:23,039
Don't worry.

20
00:02:23,039 --> 00:02:24,359
It's impossible...

21
00:02:24,359 --> 00:02:26,339
for anyone in our family to get sick.

22
00:02:26,339 --> 00:02:29,639
Besides, this illness will subside
in a few days.

23
00:02:29,639 --> 00:02:30,679
I'm off.

24
00:02:30,679 --> 00:02:32,968
I'm going to study now!

25
00:03:04,440 --> 00:03:05,480
Found it!

26
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:07,665
It's my brother's handwriting.

27
00:03:11,298 --> 00:03:13,080
40 miles southeast of Xiangyang City.

28
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,839
Eagle Beak Rock in Flying Petals Col.

29
00:03:14,839 --> 00:03:16,440
Qingyu Grass grows on the precipice.

30
00:03:16,440 --> 00:03:17,919
It blooms for three to five days.

31
00:03:17,919 --> 00:03:20,160
Multi-tailed nocturnal moths live inside,

32
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,520
weaving cocoons within the flower buds.

33
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,920
When the cocoon is about to break,

34
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:24,119
remove the flower bud.

35
00:03:24,119 --> 00:03:26,880
The moth dies at dawn,
merging into one with the cocoon.

36
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:28,919
Highly toxic, yet usable as medicine.

37
00:03:28,919 --> 00:03:31,199
Recorded in the ancient scrolls of Lament Pill.

38
00:03:31,199 --> 00:03:34,240
Used as a medicinal booster,
it can cure all kinds of rare poisons.

39
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:36,360
Formed at dawn and withered at dusk,

40
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,600
named the Day-Long Cocoon.

41
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:42,412
So this Day-Long Cocoon
is an ingredient for Lament Pill.

42
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:45,880
This herb opens on sunny days
and closes on rainy days.

43
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:47,440
Over ten feet above the ground,

44
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:49,199
it is occasionally seen on cliffs.

45
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:51,919
To harvest the Day-Long Cocoon,
seal it in a jade box with gold leaf.

46
00:03:51,919 --> 00:03:55,725
Store it in a cold, dark place,
and it will stay fresh for three days.

47
00:03:55,725 --> 00:03:57,720
Store it in a dark place,

48
00:03:57,720 --> 00:04:00,037
and it will stay fresh for three days.

49
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:18,039
You...

50
00:04:18,039 --> 00:04:22,949
You can't take me away!
On what grounds? Do you have evidence?

51
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:34,050
It should be in the well.

52
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:33,440
It really is the Day-Long Cocoon.

53
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:35,639
No wonder my brother was so certain...

54
00:05:35,639 --> 00:05:38,560
he'd win the Suwen Assembly.

55
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:40,720
Lament Pill has been lost for years.

56
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:43,759
With this, there's a chance
to concoct Lament Pill.

57
00:05:43,759 --> 00:05:45,800
That night, my brother...

58
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:49,750
really was waiting on the cliff
at Flying Petals Col all night.

59
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:53,600
He must have said so in court,

60
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,920
but no one believed him.

61
00:05:56,559 --> 00:06:00,075
He didn't tell anyone
where the cocoon was hidden,

62
00:06:00,075 --> 00:06:02,600
likely fearing the evidence would be ruined.

63
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:05,338
If I had gone to the county court then,

64
00:06:05,999 --> 00:06:08,812
he would have told me everything.

65
00:06:09,999 --> 00:06:12,441
I should have attended the trial.

66
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:15,224
I should have gone.

67
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:19,072
There were so many medicinal herbs

68
00:06:19,072 --> 00:06:20,999
planted in
the garden,

69
00:06:20,999 --> 00:06:23,359
yet he never bothered to look at them.

70
00:06:24,359 --> 00:06:26,999
Why did he suddenly study so hard?

71
00:06:27,999 --> 00:06:30,119
Why did he risk his life...

72
00:06:30,119 --> 00:06:32,280
to gather herbs in the mountains?

73
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:34,050
The reason...

74
00:06:34,050 --> 00:06:36,600
He already told you that.

75
00:06:40,919 --> 00:06:43,337
It was I who didn't give him a chance.

76
00:06:53,400 --> 00:06:56,080
If I had believed in his innocence...

77
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:59,485
and cherished his belongings,

78
00:07:01,999 --> 00:07:04,962
we might have found that missing page long ago.

79
00:07:07,439 --> 00:07:09,812
It was I who didn't believe him.

80
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:28,472
[Drinks and Dishes][Guest Lounge]

81
00:07:59,359 --> 00:08:02,239
Why was my brother so certain...

82
00:08:02,239 --> 00:08:05,280
that the plague would end in a few days?

83
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:06,960
Was he looking for the cocoon

84
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:08,479
because of the plague?

85
00:08:08,479 --> 00:08:10,160
I suspect so as well.

86
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:13,619
The Day-Long Cocoon is highly toxic.
Lament Pill can cure rare poisons

87
00:08:13,619 --> 00:08:15,160
and bring
back lives

88
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:17,840
by fighting poison with poison.

89
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:21,160
I remember Jin Zhen Ping claimed to the public.

90
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:24,520
The plague was caused
by seasonal irregularities.

91
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:27,212
Then why would he need the Day-Long Cocoon?

92
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:33,680
The so-called plague

93
00:08:33,680 --> 00:08:35,550
was actually caused by poisoning.

94
00:08:35,550 --> 00:08:38,679
[Jiao Mansion]

95
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:42,840
I do enjoy working on these embroideries.

96
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:46,680
However, the pattern you mentioned...

97
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:48,880
I've never seen before.

98
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:52,879
You don't seem interested in needlework.

99
00:08:52,879 --> 00:08:55,360
Why ask so suddenly?

100
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:58,135
It's for my auntie's case.

101
00:09:01,280 --> 00:09:02,679
Aunt.

102
00:09:02,679 --> 00:09:05,960
On the night of the incident,
it was still raining.

103
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:08,985
Did you see Jin Xue Wen's face clearly?

104
00:09:10,119 --> 00:09:12,400
That man...

105
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:16,679
looked like a scholar from a distance.

106
00:09:16,679 --> 00:09:19,200
He looked exactly like him.

107
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:21,800
Was there anything unusual about him?

108
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:24,388
Like the way he walked.

109
00:09:28,999 --> 00:09:31,893
It's been far too long.

110
00:09:34,999 --> 00:09:38,799
Madam, the young master has arrived.
He's in the front yard.

111
00:09:38,799 --> 00:09:40,663
Si Yuan.

112
00:09:41,239 --> 00:09:43,320
Why is he here?

113
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:45,760
Then I will leave you be, Aunt.

114
00:09:45,760 --> 00:09:48,054
I'll visit you next time.

115
00:09:48,919 --> 00:09:51,160
Ling Long, don't leave now.

116
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:54,239
It's a good chance for you to meet Si Yuan.

117
00:09:54,239 --> 00:09:58,062
Technically, he is your cousin.

118
00:09:58,062 --> 00:09:59,726
Mother.

119
00:10:00,386 --> 00:10:01,400
Si Yuan,

120
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:02,760
this is your cousin.

121
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:04,559
Uncle Huo's daughter.

122
00:10:04,559 --> 00:10:07,837
Ling Long, this is my son, Si Yuan.

123
00:10:07,837 --> 00:10:09,725
Greetings, Cousin.

124
00:10:14,159 --> 00:10:17,312
I didn't expect to meet you today.

125
00:10:17,312 --> 00:10:20,399
[Jiao Si Yuan, Young Master of Shengyun]
My late father often spoke of you.

126
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:23,112
He praised you as a person of great talent.

127
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:27,279
Ling Long,

128
00:10:27,279 --> 00:10:29,587
so you knew your uncle?

129
00:10:29,587 --> 00:10:31,080
I have...

130
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:33,062
met him before.

131
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:36,112
I've crossed swords with him.

132
00:10:43,119 --> 00:10:45,279
The illness was very strange.

133
00:10:45,279 --> 00:10:49,080
Those who were constantly out
didn't necessarily get sick.

134
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:51,359
But for those who never left their homes,

135
00:10:51,359 --> 00:10:54,680
their entire families might have died.

136
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:56,280
In the east end of our town,

137
00:10:56,280 --> 00:10:58,912
few caught it.

138
00:10:58,912 --> 00:11:01,775
But many died in the west end.

139
00:11:02,479 --> 00:11:07,639
Now the people living by the West River
have all moved here in recent years.

140
00:11:07,639 --> 00:11:09,680
You can go ask him.

141
00:11:09,680 --> 00:11:11,960
I heard his whole family caught that disease.

142
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:14,400
Not a single one survived.

143
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:16,720
When the plague broke out,

144
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:18,920
I was working out of town.

145
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:20,999
By the time I got the news and returned,

146
00:11:20,999 --> 00:11:23,639
my family had been taken
deep into the mountains.

147
00:11:23,639 --> 00:11:26,879
A few days later,
they told me everyone was gone.

148
00:11:26,879 --> 00:11:28,600
Later, I also caught it.

149
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:31,920
Thanks to the Jin family, I managed to survive.

150
00:11:31,920 --> 00:11:34,450
What were the symptoms when it flared up?

151
00:11:35,159 --> 00:11:36,359
So weird.

152
00:11:36,359 --> 00:11:38,399
It felt like I was in a dream.

153
00:11:38,399 --> 00:11:40,639
I had endless energy.

154
00:11:40,639 --> 00:11:43,440
One moment, I'd see my late wife,

155
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:45,279
and the next, I'd see my child.

156
00:11:45,279 --> 00:11:46,640
After I woke up,

157
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:48,119
I had no idea what I'd done.

158
00:11:48,119 --> 00:11:49,880
The symptoms he described sound like

159
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:52,519
the effects of Yemotian Poison.

160
00:11:52,519 --> 00:11:55,587
More like the Seven-Day Drunken Dream
that Tang mentioned.

161
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:58,440
If...

162
00:11:58,440 --> 00:12:01,787
the plague your brother found
was actually caused by poisoning,

163
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:04,960
then it's highly likely...

164
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:07,062
he was silenced.

165
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:18,975
So that's how it was.

166
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,773
Anyhow,

167
00:12:21,773 --> 00:12:23,440
it's his fault.

168
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:26,639
He's your elder,
yet he makes things hard for you.

169
00:12:26,639 --> 00:12:28,359
I'm sorry, Aunt.

170
00:12:28,359 --> 00:12:29,766
Earlier,

171
00:12:29,766 --> 00:12:31,920
I kept this from you.

172
00:12:31,920 --> 00:12:32,920
It's no matter.

173
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:35,480
You and my father...

174
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:38,040
crossed swords more than once, right?

175
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:56,575
Since he already lost to you,

176
00:12:57,159 --> 00:13:02,012
why did you have to be so ruthless
and take his life?

177
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:06,525
At such a young age,

178
00:13:06,525 --> 00:13:09,119
to be so cruel?

179
00:13:09,119 --> 00:13:12,560
- Do you suspect that I killed--
- My father was killed by a sword

180
00:13:12,560 --> 00:13:16,512
pierced through the Baihui point on his head.

181
00:13:16,512 --> 00:13:20,475
And his swordplay has always been fast.

182
00:13:20,475 --> 00:13:21,600
Cousin,

183
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:23,600
tell me, in this martial world,

184
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,840
how many have such lightness skill?

185
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:28,680
To dodge his sword during a battle,

186
00:13:28,680 --> 00:13:30,359
and leap to a high position immediately,

187
00:13:30,359 --> 00:13:34,550
leaving him no time to defend
before being killed with one strike.

188
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:37,320
This move...

189
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:42,120
it looks like your Linglong Manor's
A Fleeting Glimpse.

190
00:13:44,119 --> 00:13:45,399
And you,

191
00:13:45,399 --> 00:13:48,325
you were in Xiangyang at the time.

192
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:51,125
Weren't you?

193
00:13:52,359 --> 00:13:53,359
Cousin,

194
00:13:53,359 --> 00:13:55,320
I understand your suspicion.

195
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:57,879
But I did not do this.

196
00:13:57,879 --> 00:14:01,440
Uncle was brought to Xiangyang
by Jing Yi Ming's assassins.

197
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:04,721
Those men have mastered
the ultimate moves of various sects.

198
00:14:05,399 --> 00:14:06,840
Regarding Uncle's death...

199
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:09,784
you might need to find clues from them.

200
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:14,387
So that's how it is.

201
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:18,195
Thank you for telling me.

202
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:20,999
Ling Long.

203
00:14:20,999 --> 00:14:22,800
Why don't you go back now?

204
00:14:22,800 --> 00:14:25,250
I'll talk to your cousin.

205
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:56,250
Vegetables! Fresh vegetables!

206
00:15:09,920 --> 00:15:11,575
Brother.

207
00:15:13,879 --> 00:15:15,560
Since you agreed to come home with me,

208
00:15:15,560 --> 00:15:18,650
why did you sneak back here without telling me?

209
00:15:21,239 --> 00:15:22,680
By the way, Brother,

210
00:15:22,680 --> 00:15:25,159
I have something urgent to ask.

211
00:15:25,159 --> 00:15:26,359
[Grace Extends To All Quarters]
You want me to search for

212
00:15:26,359 --> 00:15:29,212
[Integrity and Diligence]
the prescription for the plague back then?

213
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:36,080
Are you still investigating Jiu Lang's case?

214
00:15:36,080 --> 00:15:39,960
- Why bring up that plague again?
- This is a grave matter.

215
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:41,600
Please help us, Fourth Aunt.

216
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:45,359
But I really don't know
where San Lang kept that prescription.

217
00:15:45,359 --> 00:15:48,320
Jin Zhen Ping knew you gave us
Yemotian's antidote.

218
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:49,800
Did he give you a hard time?

219
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:51,550
No.

220
00:15:52,639 --> 00:15:54,400
No.

221
00:15:57,560 --> 00:15:59,462
Forget it.

222
00:15:59,462 --> 00:16:01,775
I'll think of another way.

223
00:16:03,839 --> 00:16:04,960
Fourth Lady.

224
00:16:04,960 --> 00:16:06,239
Have you ever seen...

225
00:16:06,239 --> 00:16:08,886
the wonder of the late spring
flowers at Flying Petals Col?

226
00:16:08,886 --> 00:16:11,400
Have you seen any woman

227
00:16:11,400 --> 00:16:14,344
with this floral pattern embroidered
on her dress?

228
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:20,720
Is this...

229
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:23,262
also related to the case?

230
00:16:29,040 --> 00:16:31,687
Then I must think it through.

231
00:16:32,479 --> 00:16:34,577
Fourth Aunt!

232
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:40,440
Fourth Aunt.

233
00:16:40,440 --> 00:16:42,800
The decoction the kitchen
prepared for you is ready.

234
00:16:42,800 --> 00:16:45,712
Please take it immediately.

235
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:48,664
Alright.

236
00:16:55,239 --> 00:16:56,800
Little Seventeen.

237
00:16:56,800 --> 00:16:58,800
Fourth Aunt is getting on in years.

238
00:16:58,800 --> 00:17:01,440
She should be enjoying a peaceful life.

239
00:17:02,160 --> 00:17:05,266
You'd better not cause her any trouble.

240
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:14,879
Jiao Chao Gui was definitely
not killed by Linglong Manor.

241
00:17:14,879 --> 00:17:17,359
So it really was Jing Yi Ming's men.

242
00:17:17,359 --> 00:17:19,560
Did Jiao Si Yuan cause you any trouble?

243
00:17:19,560 --> 00:17:20,999
- Do you need me to--
- No need.

244
00:17:20,999 --> 00:17:22,759
I've already explained it to him.

245
00:17:22,759 --> 00:17:24,119
Ling Long.

246
00:17:24,119 --> 00:17:25,359
It is dangerous here.

247
00:17:25,359 --> 00:17:27,359
You should come home with me.

248
00:17:27,359 --> 00:17:28,999
I was wrong before.

249
00:17:28,999 --> 00:17:31,080
I shouldn't have said those things.

250
00:17:31,080 --> 00:17:32,720
It's not that Father doesn't care about Auntie.

251
00:17:32,720 --> 00:17:34,320
It's just that...

252
00:17:34,320 --> 00:17:36,239
there's just so much he can't help.

253
00:17:36,239 --> 00:17:38,036
Don't blame him.

254
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:40,759
There's something fishy about Auntie's case.

255
00:17:40,759 --> 00:17:43,125
I must keep going.

256
00:17:43,125 --> 00:17:44,479
Give me some time.

257
00:17:44,479 --> 00:17:46,440
When the case is closed,

258
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:48,475
I will go home.

259
00:17:59,519 --> 00:18:01,119
Brother, don't worry.

260
00:18:01,119 --> 00:18:03,080
Since I've decided to break the engagement,

261
00:18:03,080 --> 00:18:05,475
I will give Father a proper explanation.

262
00:18:06,080 --> 00:18:08,560
Anyway, I will never marry Shao Ji Zu.

263
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:12,000
That man is foolish, arrogant, and conceited!

264
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:14,087
I truly despise him.

265
00:18:14,087 --> 00:18:15,600
As for Father,

266
00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:16,800
I'll calm her down.

267
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:17,999
In short,

268
00:18:17,999 --> 00:18:20,400
once the truth is out, you must return home.

269
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:23,520
Otherwise, he will come to find you himself.

270
00:18:24,600 --> 00:18:25,720
Let's go.

271
00:18:25,720 --> 00:18:27,537
I'll see you back to the inn.

272
00:18:44,639 --> 00:18:46,300
Get up!

273
00:18:58,960 --> 00:19:00,933
All of you, get out.

274
00:19:13,919 --> 00:19:16,787
You've seen Huo Ling Long?

275
00:19:21,600 --> 00:19:23,520
Who does she think she is?

276
00:19:23,520 --> 00:19:24,679
And that Huo Feng.

277
00:19:24,679 --> 00:19:26,520
If not for His Lordship,
I would've killed him already!

278
00:19:26,520 --> 00:19:27,879
Enough.

279
00:19:27,879 --> 00:19:29,600
The wedding is approaching.

280
00:19:29,600 --> 00:19:32,719
Once you've married her
and got the Linglong Eye,

281
00:19:32,719 --> 00:19:37,550
- you'll have rendered great service to him.
- Married her?

282
00:19:38,159 --> 00:19:40,600
Like she would return to Linglong Manor.

283
00:19:45,080 --> 00:19:48,937
There are plenty of ways to get her home.

284
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:53,987
It depends on whether you've got the nerve.

285
00:20:00,987 --> 00:20:04,945
[Tang Stronghold]

286
00:20:15,480 --> 00:20:17,399
[Cure the root, not the branch]
Cure the root,

287
00:20:17,399 --> 00:20:20,650
not the branch.

288
00:20:32,439 --> 00:20:33,760
Since you prefer the shade,

289
00:20:33,760 --> 00:20:36,450
I'll put you in the attic.

290
00:20:38,320 --> 00:20:39,480
I know...

291
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:41,639
you prefer the sun.

292
00:20:41,639 --> 00:20:43,760
Get some sunlight.

293
00:20:43,760 --> 00:20:46,157
Now look at this pot.

294
00:20:46,959 --> 00:20:48,000
My Lord.

295
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:51,399
We've asked all the embroidery workshops,
tailors, and clothing shops in town.

296
00:20:51,399 --> 00:20:53,550
No one has seen this pattern.

297
00:20:55,760 --> 00:20:58,119
Could that woman have embroidered it herself?

298
00:20:58,119 --> 00:21:01,719
My Fourth Aunt knows many ladies
from prestigious families in town.

299
00:21:01,719 --> 00:21:04,080
Perhaps we can get some clues from her.

300
00:21:04,080 --> 00:21:05,760
But Jin Zhen Ping...

301
00:21:05,760 --> 00:21:07,600
If we show up at the door to ask,

302
00:21:07,600 --> 00:21:10,000
it would be putting her in a difficult spot.

303
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:12,800
Then bypass Jin Zhen Ping and ask her secretly.

304
00:21:12,800 --> 00:21:14,840
Leave this to me.

305
00:21:14,840 --> 00:21:17,835
[Joyful Stay Inn]

306
00:21:41,119 --> 00:21:43,512
It's the water.

307
00:21:56,199 --> 00:21:59,425
Tang Sect wanted Yemotian in the first place.

308
00:21:59,425 --> 00:22:01,487
Seven-Day Drunken Dream...

309
00:22:01,487 --> 00:22:03,350
was an accident.

310
00:22:03,350 --> 00:22:05,925
[Jin Mansion]

311
00:22:15,784 --> 00:22:16,919
Miss Huo.

312
00:22:16,919 --> 00:22:19,119
I need to talk to the Fourth Lady.

313
00:22:19,119 --> 00:22:21,354
Please wait a moment.

314
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:30,240
[Gace Covers All Living Beings]

315
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:32,200
Madam. Miss Huo is here.

316
00:22:32,200 --> 00:22:34,272
She wishes to see you.

317
00:22:38,600 --> 00:22:41,240
Tell her to wait outside for a moment.

318
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:43,039
Yes.

319
00:22:50,120 --> 00:22:55,240
[Empty Light Chamber]

320
00:23:31,879 --> 00:23:34,837
Spring-longing should not strive
with flowers to break forth.‌

321
00:23:39,879 --> 00:23:41,790
Chunxin Pavilion.

322
00:23:51,275 --> 00:23:52,575
[Settle in Calm, Stay with Joy]

323
00:23:55,040 --> 00:23:56,625
Impossible.

324
00:23:56,625 --> 00:23:57,639
Absolutely impossible.

325
00:23:57,639 --> 00:23:59,359
It must be a coincidence.

326
00:23:59,359 --> 00:24:01,199
My fourth aunt has been married
in Xiangyang for over 20 years.

327
00:24:01,199 --> 00:24:02,520
She must have visited Flying Petals Col.

328
00:24:02,520 --> 00:24:05,520
What's so strange about her
embroidering flying petals?

329
00:24:05,520 --> 00:24:07,439
But the man and woman in the picture...

330
00:24:07,439 --> 00:24:09,480
They match the hunter's description.

331
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:11,240
It must be a coincidence.

332
00:24:11,240 --> 00:24:12,520
She's not that kind of person.

333
00:24:12,520 --> 00:24:15,040
She's a good person.

334
00:24:15,040 --> 00:24:16,920
Don't panic.

335
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:19,050
We'll go back and ask.

336
00:24:19,050 --> 00:24:21,050
Let's go now.

337
00:24:22,919 --> 00:24:27,983
Tell me. Does the Fourth Lady have
a white dress with pale red petals on it?

338
00:24:27,983 --> 00:24:30,399
Yes, I was tidying the room one day,

339
00:24:30,399 --> 00:24:32,520
that dress was at the bottom of a chest.

340
00:24:32,520 --> 00:24:36,159
I wanted to take it out to air it,
but Cai Zhu scolded me for it.

341
00:24:36,159 --> 00:24:37,639
Where is the Fourth Lady now?

342
00:24:37,639 --> 00:24:40,580
She has gone to pray at Moyun Temple.

343
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:46,000
Where is Moyun Temple?

344
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:47,159
Is it far from Flying Petals Col?

345
00:24:47,159 --> 00:24:48,399
About 30 miles from the city.

346
00:24:48,399 --> 00:24:50,919
And another seven or eight miles
past Flying Petals Col.

347
00:24:50,919 --> 00:24:52,959
Are both places in the same direction?

348
00:24:52,959 --> 00:24:54,800
More or less.

349
00:24:57,600 --> 00:25:00,875
You mean she didn't actually go pray?

350
00:25:08,237 --> 00:25:14,237
[Moyun Temple]

351
00:25:15,359 --> 00:25:16,959
Why did she enter the temple?

352
00:25:16,959 --> 00:25:19,097
Could we have been wrong?

353
00:25:19,679 --> 00:25:20,879
Your heart is in turmoil.

354
00:25:20,879 --> 00:25:22,647
So as your mind.

355
00:25:23,320 --> 00:25:25,159
That's the Jin family's coachman.

356
00:25:25,159 --> 00:25:29,370
You think she would let her own coachman
drive her to meet Tang Ji?

357
00:25:31,520 --> 00:25:34,111
So she's switching carriages.

358
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:40,320
Why did she change out of the clothes?

359
00:25:40,320 --> 00:25:44,360
Could she have spotted us
and tried to destroy it?

360
00:25:47,840 --> 00:25:49,399
That dress is vital evidence.

361
00:25:49,399 --> 00:25:52,087
I'll go find it. You two follow her.

362
00:27:37,240 --> 00:27:39,359
Miss Huo.

363
00:27:39,359 --> 00:27:40,560
Why are you burning joss paper?

364
00:27:40,560 --> 00:27:44,487
The Fourth Lady ordered it.
I don't know who it's for.

365
00:27:45,320 --> 00:27:46,359
However...

366
00:27:46,359 --> 00:27:49,439
She kept muttering,

367
00:27:49,439 --> 00:27:52,062
"I'm sorry, Little Seventeen."

368
00:28:17,720 --> 00:28:20,000
So they didn't just meet at Chunxin Pavilion.

369
00:28:20,000 --> 00:28:22,605
They even set up such a secret hideout.

370
00:28:23,199 --> 00:28:25,719
Where did the Fourth Lady go?

371
00:28:25,719 --> 00:28:28,187
There must be another exit here.

372
00:28:50,679 --> 00:28:52,700
I hear water.

373
00:28:58,399 --> 00:29:00,825
There should be an underground river below.

374
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:08,040
Besides the entrance we just came through,

375
00:29:08,040 --> 00:29:10,040
there must be another air vent here,

376
00:29:10,040 --> 00:29:12,263
or there wouldn't be any wind.

377
00:29:27,399 --> 00:29:29,181
It's poison!

378
00:29:49,600 --> 00:29:52,159
So you didn't believe what I said earlier.

379
00:29:52,159 --> 00:29:55,237
Save it to explain to my father.

380
00:30:00,760 --> 00:30:04,979
When your father fought me,
he used this same sword formation.

381
00:30:05,840 --> 00:30:07,919
You were able to break it before

382
00:30:07,919 --> 00:30:10,159
only because Zhan Zhao was helping you.

383
00:30:10,159 --> 00:30:11,399
But now,

384
00:30:11,399 --> 00:30:13,625
your helper is gone.

385
00:30:35,159 --> 00:30:38,399
Fourth Aunt actually conspired
with Tang Ji to trap me!

386
00:30:38,399 --> 00:30:39,879
She knows you're immune to poison.

387
00:30:39,879 --> 00:30:42,560
- Why would she still use it?
- To deal with you, of course.

388
00:30:42,560 --> 00:30:45,399
Without you,
dealing with me would be much easier.

389
00:30:45,399 --> 00:30:48,487
I never guarded against Fourth Aunt.

390
00:31:00,560 --> 00:31:03,159
Tang Ji, you hypocrite!

391
00:31:03,159 --> 00:31:04,679
First you framed my brother,

392
00:31:04,679 --> 00:31:07,062
and now you want to kill me!

393
00:31:10,280 --> 00:31:11,320
Bai Yu Tang!

394
00:31:11,320 --> 00:31:12,919
That poison wasn't meant for me.

395
00:31:12,919 --> 00:31:15,719
They want to make you hallucinate!

396
00:31:15,719 --> 00:31:18,840
Neither you nor Zhan Zhao
will leave Flying Petals Col today.

397
00:31:18,840 --> 00:31:21,679
The truth about your brother
will never be revealed.

398
00:31:21,679 --> 00:31:24,913
You'll always be the brother of a murderer.

399
00:31:33,119 --> 00:31:34,119
Bai Yu Tang!

400
00:31:34,119 --> 00:31:36,687
Look carefully! Who am I?

401
00:31:36,687 --> 00:31:38,359
Even if you kill me,

402
00:31:38,359 --> 00:31:40,080
your brother won't be alive.

403
00:31:40,080 --> 00:31:41,560
You can never overturn the case!

404
00:31:41,560 --> 00:31:46,025
Jin Xue Wen will always be a despised murderer!

405
00:31:49,719 --> 00:31:51,720
Bai Yu Tang! I'm not Tang Ji.

406
00:31:51,720 --> 00:31:53,614
I'm Zhan Zhao!

407
00:32:08,439 --> 00:32:10,600
I've already done...

408
00:32:10,600 --> 00:32:12,625
what you asked.

409
00:32:14,320 --> 00:32:16,725
Let's not meet again.

410
00:33:30,280 --> 00:33:33,388
She's still useful to me.

411
00:33:33,959 --> 00:33:35,959
Take your men and get lost.

412
00:33:35,959 --> 00:33:37,879
You hurt my subordinates.

413
00:33:37,879 --> 00:33:40,375
You think you can dismiss me with a word?

414
00:33:41,199 --> 00:33:43,000
You don't want to leave?

415
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:45,647
Then all of you stay here.

416
00:34:33,240 --> 00:34:35,080
Little Bai!

417
00:34:35,080 --> 00:34:36,675
Brother.

418
00:34:38,679 --> 00:34:40,240
It's really you.

419
00:34:40,240 --> 00:34:41,937
Shoot!

420
00:35:19,959 --> 00:35:22,958
Set the whole cave on fire!

421
00:35:47,839 --> 00:35:51,759
Brother, it's burning outside! Don't go out!

422
00:35:51,759 --> 00:35:54,440
Bai Yu Tang, wake up!

423
00:35:54,440 --> 00:35:56,240
I'm a grown man.

424
00:35:56,240 --> 00:35:57,920
I will definitely save you.

425
00:35:57,920 --> 00:35:59,560
I was wrong.

426
00:35:59,560 --> 00:36:01,319
I've been wrong for 15 years.

427
00:36:01,319 --> 00:36:03,719
This time, I must save you!

428
00:36:03,719 --> 00:36:05,412
I know.

429
00:36:05,412 --> 00:36:08,124
We'll definitely escape this.

430
00:36:09,040 --> 00:36:10,920
Guard the exit well.

431
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:12,719
I want them to be...

432
00:36:12,719 --> 00:36:15,040
burned to ashes.

433
00:36:15,040 --> 00:36:16,829
Yes, sir!

434
00:36:28,480 --> 00:36:30,362
I hear water.

435
00:36:32,639 --> 00:36:35,240
There should be
an underground river below.

436
00:36:35,240 --> 00:36:37,176
Follow me.

437
00:37:09,159 --> 00:37:10,762
Zhan Zhao.

438
00:37:31,639 --> 00:37:33,962
Take them. Let's go.

439
00:37:45,680 --> 00:37:48,040
Commander Shao,
you've finally avenged yourself.

440
00:37:48,040 --> 00:37:49,988
Are you satisfied now?

441
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:53,159
Ling Long, you know me best.

442
00:37:53,159 --> 00:37:56,987
Our childhood friendship wasn't for nothing.

443
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:00,780
Let's go.

444
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:03,537
I'll take you home.

445
00:38:12,880 --> 00:38:16,184
Zhan. I'll leave this to you.
I'm off to get someone.

446
00:38:17,000 --> 00:38:20,377
What a mess Tang Ji has made!

447
00:39:41,600 --> 00:39:44,240
What? Aren't you going to help Huo Xiao Mei?

448
00:39:44,240 --> 00:39:47,252
She's no longer Huo Xiao Di anymore.

449
00:40:04,119 --> 00:40:05,799
I just want to ask you,

450
00:40:05,799 --> 00:40:08,675
why are you so sure I'm the murderer?

451
00:40:08,675 --> 00:40:12,021
[Moyun Temple]

452
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:28,637
You...

453
00:40:30,350 --> 00:40:32,520
You're not dead?

454
00:40:32,520 --> 00:40:35,840
Then... where is Tang Ji?

455
00:40:36,839 --> 00:40:39,799
You're still thinking about that adulterer now?

456
00:40:39,799 --> 00:40:41,119
I...

457
00:40:41,119 --> 00:40:43,453
My fourth uncle was a bit eccentric,

458
00:40:43,453 --> 00:40:47,600
- but he was so good to you.
- I was wrong! I was wrong!

459
00:40:47,600 --> 00:40:50,600
Tang Ji and I have known each other
since childhood.

460
00:40:50,600 --> 00:40:52,440
We were in love.

461
00:40:52,440 --> 00:40:54,759
But our statuses were different.

462
00:40:54,759 --> 00:40:58,575
My parents forced me
to marry into the Jin family.

463
00:41:03,360 --> 00:41:05,000
That cave today...

464
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:07,520
Tang Ji set it up on short notice,

465
00:41:07,520 --> 00:41:09,722
so he could lure us into a trap?

466
00:41:12,319 --> 00:41:13,432
Yes.

467
00:41:13,432 --> 00:41:16,480
He said you kept expanding
what you were looking into.

468
00:41:16,480 --> 00:41:18,680
Sooner or later,

469
00:41:18,680 --> 00:41:20,400
you would find out about us.

470
00:41:20,400 --> 00:41:23,940
You're just afraid
that your affair would be exposed?

471
00:41:24,560 --> 00:41:28,867
Even now, you still won't tell the truth!

472
00:41:31,562 --> 00:41:34,080
15 years ago,

473
00:41:34,080 --> 00:41:38,400
was it you or Tang Ji
who concocted the Seven-Day Drunken Dream,

474
00:41:38,400 --> 00:41:40,520
causing countless deaths in Tanxi Town?

475
00:41:40,520 --> 00:41:45,275
Was it you or Tang Ji
who killed my brother to cover it up?

476
00:41:47,080 --> 00:41:52,000
You let me stay in the Jin family
just so you could watch me.

477
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:57,400
You brought out Jin Zhen Ping's manuscript
and mentioned my brother's confession

478
00:41:57,400 --> 00:42:00,750
just so I'd take the antidote and leave,
giving up on the case!

479
00:42:00,750 --> 00:42:01,799
I...

480
00:42:01,799 --> 00:42:04,440
Whenever we mentioned Jin Zhen Ping
colluding with the Tang Sect,

481
00:42:04,440 --> 00:42:06,000
you were always evasive.

482
00:42:06,000 --> 00:42:08,239
It wasn't for the Jin family's reputation,

483
00:42:08,239 --> 00:42:11,727
but to keep your scandalous affair hidden!

484
00:42:12,520 --> 00:42:15,880
We didn't intend to harm anyone.

485
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:17,759
It was just an accident.

486
00:42:17,759 --> 00:42:20,440
I know I've harmed so many people.

487
00:42:20,440 --> 00:42:22,000
My death would not be a loss.

488
00:42:22,000 --> 00:42:24,239
It's only right that you kill me.

489
00:42:24,239 --> 00:42:26,360
Little Seventeen...

490
00:42:26,360 --> 00:42:28,575
Little Seventeen. Please.

491
00:42:28,575 --> 00:42:31,520
Can you spare me some dignity?

492
00:42:31,520 --> 00:42:34,680
Don't let the Jins know about this.

493
00:42:42,400 --> 00:42:44,600
This is between you and her.

494
00:42:44,600 --> 00:42:46,360
How to deal with her...

495
00:42:46,360 --> 00:42:48,303
is up to you.
